  "body": "<img alt=\"20a-IMG_9122.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889082430-GOB4WZKTFQ0VW6418AU6/20a-IMG_9122.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20b-IMG_9111.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889082483-Z3KNCFCPA86OWZQ8TKZD/20b-IMG_9111.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20c-IMG_9109.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889083674-TT4RHY1WO3CPBB8037FY/20c-IMG_9109.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-IMG_9119.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889084674-YIEGUHVS0FIGOAEY5NIQ/20d-IMG_9119.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-IMG_9117.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889085943-FEEL67J4D6HB7YZFUJ5U/20e-IMG_9117.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-IMG_9115.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889086722-LSI6X376IU03XV17CV1K/20f-IMG_9115.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20g-IMG_9113.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889087392-UR3SN740CFEFALG2ZLVY/20g-IMG_9113.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20h-IMG_9107-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599889087269-IUQ5O0SAC0Y92SRC9XC8/20h-IMG_9107-600x400.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Today I am sharing some fun sneak peeks at the layouts I made using Studio Calico's June scrapbook kit, <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/sneak_peek?aff=6cc2c70f\">Roundabout</a>. I was especially in love with all the bright colors and travel-themed ephemera featured in this kit! I got all the scrapbook add-ons and also the Project Life kit. The box for that PL kit? Droolworthy. Roundabout will be available for purchase on May 27th at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a> - you don't want to miss it!</p>"
